This LDS yurt is embedded in the Szîvküldi Lakótelep, the VR social housing neighborhood that I’ve been growing since 2018. I established my LDS career with the aim to roll as far as I can in 2015. LDS NFTs are offerings of the energy of tumbling to help manifest the grandmother spirit.
